  <div class="subfield">
    <strong>$2 - Source</strong>

    <div class="description">
      MARC code that identifies the source of the term or code
      used to record the carrier type information.
    </div>

    <div class="description2 description">
      Code from: <a href=
      "http://www.loc.gov/standards/sourcelist/genre-form.html"><em>Genre/Form Code and Term Source Codes</em></a>.
    </div>

